data.text: @CryptosR_Us Moreover, Tarek is a real lousy negotiator. Not unlike someone that will remain unnamed.
@CryptosR_Us I watch so many of them shows im thinking I can flip houses funny we all watch the same stuff....

@CryptosR_Us There’s been many similar shows over the years. The sale prices and dates when they are sold are public record.  They used to give out the address of homes seen on the show, but people posted online when checked they either sold for less or didn’t sell at all.  Not so easy.
@CryptosR_Us Imagine if u were the contractor and u flipped the homes and had ur guys do the work. That’s when it’s really pot odds in ur favor.  Cut out the middle man
@CryptosR_Us Gorge I was just thinking the same thing .. their prices are grossly inflated. Unlike the desert flippers’ contractors.
